column26:
Email about the created account is not being sent to the newly added user on registered email id

Steps to reproduce :-

#  Go to application
# Do log in process by using valid credentials
# Go to ‘Users’ module
# Go to ‘Add New User’ page by clicking on ‘Add New’ link under ‘Users’ module
# Verify ‘Send User Notification’ checkbox by selecting it 

Expected Result :-

Email about the created account should be sent to the newly added user on registered email id if checkbox of ‘Send User Notification’ is selected

Actual Result :-

Email about the created account is not being sent to the newly added user on registered email id when checkbox of ‘Send User Notification’ is selected
